# CorrFarm — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local  →  cp .env.example .env.local
# Or run the interactive wizard  →  npm run setup

# ── API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Alpha Arcade live prediction markets
